ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:06:10.000Z","msg":"屌你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"058bfce0b6614defe696e162edb5d53914435556","tid":295942,"uid":63396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:09:31.000Z","msg":"你以後唔好渣車啦"},{"pid":"f94eee7e99ac2c7ddd6486a228fa701b5b06f138","tid":295942,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:11:42.000Z","msg":"轉線唔睇鏡 你都幾好野"},{"pid":"16c4ec8749c5b64cf27368e9d3887358fa826137","tid":295942,"uid":2470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:13:49.000Z","msg":"屌你老母轉線都唔望隔離學咩人渣車啊"},{"pid":"f3d2123c47bd6cd31d3d8558163f567512655d6d","tid":295942,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:15:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4abaf63869627df681a44080338068abefa822ac","tid":295942,"uid":89757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:24:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母轉線都唔望隔離學咩人渣車啊</blockquote><br />\n+1 <br />\n唔知你個咩G1咩意思<br />\n但就你完全唔識揸車仲夠膽揸出去<br />\n你不如自己賣左架車好過啦<br />\n唔撚好害人<br />\n人地都有老豆老母有仔女架<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d9b029f01a01f59c81b1966fe092c1ea42e93da","tid":295942,"uid":38946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:47:24.000Z","msg":"無信心唔好渣"},{"pid":"6d665ea2fd0ed73b2ada230e2b632d056445f2fb","tid":295942,"uid":109050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:49:52.000Z","msg":"仲害得人唔夠咩,唔好再揸車喇"},{"pid":"55f36236c5355a7d5ad606f547810b24d3194198","tid":295942,"uid":58889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:55:04.000Z","msg":"第二件老實講係有D唔好彩<br />\n但你朋友坐後座就諗住唔戴安全帶就太天真...<br />\n<br />\n第一次你自己戇鳩<br />\n第二次你朋友戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n撞完車係有陰影既,我都試過被撞, 唔敢坐車<br />\n但始終要坐, 過多排咪無事"},{"pid":"fe66e7a37f6b41cdc12af3e468d9c1e284b07291","tid":295942,"uid":108038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T12:24:57.000Z","msg":"第二次就唔關你事，無得講<br />\n但係第一次單野，你唔熟路就小心啲，揸慢啲，睇清楚先轉線<br />\n你自己撞事小，累到其他人事大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bff05e60b58801d61d5047e67a31556935bb076","tid":295942,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T12:30:58.000Z","msg":"點會高速先驚，市區難揸過高速幾倍。<br />\n高速唔好做戇鳩野，正正常常絕少出意外。市區先講反應，唔好講自己唔小心，自己好小心人地都可以叉埋黎，一失魂唔留意就撞。"}]}